Package: CompressiveNMF
Type: Package
Title: Compressive Bayesian non-negative matrix factorization for mutational signature analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Alessandro Zito
Maintainer: Alessandro Zito <azito@hsph.harvard.edu>
Description: Implements a Bayesian non-negative matrix factorization for count data. Details of the model 
             are available at in Zito and Miller (2024+), available at https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.10974
